	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-172723271" class="story-title"> <a   href="//news.slashdot.org/story/24/01/11/1646243/chicago-public-schools-lost-over-20-million-in-electronics-in-one-year-report-says">Chicago Public Schools Lost Over $20 Million In Electronics In One Year, Report Says</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.cbsnews.com/chicago/news/chicago-public-schools-lost-electronics/"  title="External link - https://www.cbsnews.com/chicago/news/chicago-public-schools-lost-electronics/" target="_blank"> (cbsnews.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
